<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>페달보드 탐색 - Dangerous Bros</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/explorer/index.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h2><img src="/images/pick.png" alt="마이페이지 아이콘" class="page-icon">
                <span class="page-title-text">페달보드 검색</span></h2>

            <div class="search-section">
                <h3>검색 옵션</h3>

                <!-- Type 4: Search by Model Name -->
                <form action="/explorer/search/model" method="GET" class="search-form">
                    <label>특정 이펙터 포함 검색 (Type 4)</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" name="modelName" placeholder="모델명 (예: TS9)" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">검색</button>
                    </div>
                </form>

                <!-- Type 5: Search by Effector Type -->
                <form action="/explorer/search/type" method="GET" class="search-form">
                    <label>이펙터 타입 포함 검색 (Type 5)</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" name="typeName" placeholder="타입 (예: Delay)" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">검색</button>
                    </div>
                </form>

                <!-- Type 6: Search by Category -->
                <form action="/explorer/search/category" method="GET" class="search-form">
                    <label>카테고리별 검색 (Type 6)</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" name="category" placeholder="카테고리 (예: Rock)" required>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">검색</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="menu-list">
                <a href="/explorer/hall-of-fame" class="menu-item">
                    <h3>🏆 명예의 전당 (Type 7)</h3>
                    <p>평점 4.5 이상인 최고의 페달보드들을 만나보세요.</p>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">메인으로</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>